{"tid":2197884,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"撐傘行山晨運  婦疑遭雷劈傷","createTime":"2020-09-11T03:03:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T04:41:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c021285877113c31f52bee1b95e7f46b4c6cacbd","tid":2197884,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T03:03:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200911/SQTEAA4CUZC3DDSNQJQKGH3F2Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200911%2FSQTEAA4CUZC3DDSNQJQKGH3F2Y%2F&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FEuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=a4d1dcbb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200911%2FSQTEAA4CUZC3DDSNQJQKGH3F2Y%2F&h=06b4342f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200911/SQTEAA4CUZC3DDSNQJQKGH3F2Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n撐傘行山晨運 <br />\n婦疑遭雷劈傷<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】昨晨雷暴警告生效期。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n昨清晨5時40分天文台發出雷暴警告，指香港局部地區有雷暴；天文台網頁顯示昨晨7時至7時59分，新界東錄得40次雲對地閃電。早上7時52分，49歲姓陳女子報警求助，指她在善明邨出發往調景嶺配水庫晨運，當行至衞奕信徑時聽到打雷巨響後不適，懷疑被雷擊中受傷。消防員尋獲女事主，當時她神智清醒，惟全身濕透，其右腰及雙腳有灼傷痕迹，消防用擔架床將她抬下山送院治理，目前情況穩定。現場消息稱，事發時下雨，女事主孭着背囊、撐雨傘擋雨。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RHfQVIK8ve0HlFYYzfd-oxOMY1Q=/1575x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TKJNDUW2TZDDZIJTXCRLA3APWM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRHfQVIK8ve0HlFYYzfd-oxOMY1Q%3D%2F1575x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTKJNDUW2TZDDZIJTXCRLA3APWM.jpg&h=7a2b4977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■一名女晨運客昨疑被雷劈傷送院。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n專家籲避免接觸金屬<br />\n<br />\n攀山專家鍾建民指，行山途中遇上雷暴應盡快前往低處，即使沒有雷暴，眼見天色轉差烏雲密佈都應盡快下山。鍾認為，遇上雷暴時應盡量避免接觸金屬，因為金屬可以導電，建議避免撐傘，並應將身上金屬物品如錶、頸鏈、爬山扣等除下，並放下行山杖。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"9990f910bda92730e1f6cfc8df391810a98077f3","tid":2197884,"uid":251119,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T03:05:28.000Z","msg":"可能係藍絲比雷劈"},{"pid":"6aaf123f3eb4ac5d9f39f6544d53de644d709a6b","tid":2197884,"uid":201237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T03:07:38.000Z","msg":"行山都唔睇天氣報告..."},{"pid":"231a96ee3c0375f1ac85cd8a3c4d1f57d01bd93b","tid":2197884,"uid":13065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T03:24:32.000Z","msg":"行開山唔睇天氣報告都算 仲要做流動避雷針。。"},{"pid":"2659b76b65074adcfee1dbf92086bee9593fbf5c","tid":2197884,"uid":38216,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T03:39:55.000Z","msg":"死唔去就有超能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddb199715ad031be7563df284280c7244944dd54","tid":2197884,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T03:42:47.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打試過俾雷劈呀 你有冇死到呀 點解佢可以唔死嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55e70d5f21f054cf18611d1566c0aa77d8a7fa33","tid":2197884,"uid":232754,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T03:50:16.000Z","msg":"咁撚弱智嘅九成九都係啲白痴藍蛆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，慶祝完可以出返去"},{"pid":"ff15ccfd5630935362b7dc1cd4ffbb8b8777ca9d","tid":2197884,"uid":293951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T03:53:19.000Z","msg":"如果係黃絲又有超能力<br />\n唔該識做 幫全香港電撚死囇個幾個"},{"pid":"c7c812169c080352e2646b10f55979dda871dccb","tid":2197884,"uid":364392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T03:59:39.000Z","msg":"死左未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61cf5392a25d62e6857b4b9e9c576c632e1fb35a","tid":2197884,"uid":35814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2